            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E4%BE%A7%E5%BC%AF%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E4%BE%A7%E5%BC%AF%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#脊柱侧弯已成危害我国儿童的第三大疾病#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E8%B6%85500%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E4%BE%A7%E5%BC%AF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E8%B6%85500%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E4%BE%A7%E5%BC%AF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#我国超500万中小学生脊柱侧弯#</span></a> 脊柱侧弯已经成为继肥胖、近视之后危害我国儿童青少年健康的第三大疾病。脊柱侧弯的产生，一般多发于儿童和青少年期，由于青春发育期进展较快，一旦被忽视，就会影响日常生活和学习。预计目前我国中小学生发生脊柱侧弯人数已经超过500万，并且还在以每年30万左右的速度递增。 <a href="http://t.cn/A6CgFf5d" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
